{"word":"H3226 - יָמִין - Yâmîyn - yaw-meen' - Jamin","slug":"H3226","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָמִין</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yâmîyn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-meen'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jamin"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>ימין</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yâmı̂yn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yaw-meen'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jamin = \"right hand\" <ol><li>the 2nd son of Simeon; founder of the family of Jaminites</li><li>a Judaite, the 2nd son of Ram the Jerahmeelite</li><li>a Levite who helped Ezra interpret the Law</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a>, <a href=\"#/H3227\">H3227</a>, <a href=\"#/H3228\">H3228</a>, <a href=\"#/H3231\">H3231</a>, <a href=\"#/H3232\">H3232</a>, <a href=\"#/H3233\">H3233</a>, <a href=\"#/H541\">H541</a>, <a href=\"#/H8486\">H8486</a>, <a href=\"#/H8487\">H8487</a>, <a href=\"#/H8488\">H8488</a>, <a href=\"#/H8489\">H8489</a>"}]}